    {
        "content": "<p>Ah, right. Then <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"bold\">E</mi><mi mathvariant=\"bold\">l</mi></mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>F</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\mathbf{El}(F)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathbf\">El</span></span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">F</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span> is the empty category.</p>",
